title: Rubio Slams Hillary Clinton’s Benghazi Failures as Secretary of State – Video 10/22/15 | Tea Party
text:
(Before It's News)
Here is Sen. Marco Rubio on “Hannity” last night where he responded to Hillary Clinton’s Benghazi testimony. Rubio said Clinton failed at every level as Secretary of State, allowing the Benghazi attack to unfold.
